&lt;li&gt;Able to travel both domestically and internationally including overnight stays&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
