&lt;li&gt;Ensure that any client complaints are forwarded to the appropriate individual(s) and ultimately resolved in a prompt and professional manner&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Closes new business and expands existing business relationships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Connects SME’s and other BD’s where added value to client is available&lt;/li&gt;
